FBIS4-40783 "drsov119__a94032" FBIS-SOV-94-119-A Daily Report 21 June 1994 ANNEX Regional Affairs Shakhray to Head Commission on Russia-Bashkir Treaty Shakhray to Head Commission on Russia-Bashkir Treaty LD1506163194 Moscow RIA in English 1313 GMT 15 Jun 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY LD1506163194 Moscow RIA English BFN [Text] Moscow, June 15, RIA -- A commission led by Sergey Shakhray has been set up to draft a bilateral treaty on the delineation and mutual delegation of powers between state authorities of the Russian Federation and the Republic of Bashkortostan. A resolution to this effect was signed by President Yeltsin, the presidential press service reports.
